Dressing: In a small bowl combine apple cider vinegar, honey, onion, mustard, salt and pepper. Slowly whisk in oil. Set aside. Salad: Finely grate or chop 2 eggs; slice remaining 2 eggs. In a large salad bowl, combine greens, tomatoes, bacon and grated eggs. Toss with dressing to coat and garnish with remaining egg slices. Serve immediately.